= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) Spell List =

This page documents all spells in '''Dragon Warrior IV''' (NES, US version).

== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior IV contains approximately 60 spells categorized into offensive, healing, support, and travel magic. Spells are learned at specific character levels.

