== Spell Data Structure ==

Each spell uses 4 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Effect type
|-
| $01 || 1 || Power/Base value
|-
| $02 || 1 || Target type
|-
| $03 || 1 || MP cost
|}

